{"tid":1024823,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"等我話俾大家聽，點解每年要搞渣打馬拉松","createTime":"2019-02-17T00:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T06:18:48.000Z","uid":123613,"like":2,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5bbec8ecd5dc33a8dbd474c6dad359c9683270","tid":1024823,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:39:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大部分中小學校每年一般1月同6月考試，考完半個月到一個月會出成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果成績唔好，咁老豆老母自然會嬲，甚至打仔，打仔係十幾廿年前仲興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為1月至2月同7月出成績表高峰期，所以有支持體罰嘅老師不如搞個體罰比賽，又叫<strong>渣打馬拉松</strong>，就係老豆老母渣住藤條去馬拉松式打仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果7月先搞馬拉松可能熱得滯，所以趁1月2月涼涼哋，等班家長睇完成績表，可以盡情馬拉松式打仔，大家話有冇道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc76930786ba0ab49ad3feb73ea5be7f1d5c7c5","tid":1024823,"uid":130019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:40:27.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"7a35c25801c952acb67b3b9cc0ed7d475d4751aa","tid":1024823,"uid":32722,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:42:05.000Z","msg":"你自己覺得好撚好笑？"},{"pid":"f997376962b5a1138fb2eebe98a973ba13c4b050","tid":1024823,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8925f32bdcdf8f2ced6bdf697ed2c30637fd92d","tid":1024823,"uid":226019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"-1/10"},{"pid":"a625371e4d4e50db3c9dbfabac69cadff194e0b0","tid":1024823,"uid":3860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"搞笑唔岩你 收手啦"},{"pid":"8c269abc73bd15dc01d48d82abc9bf4f721e4cc4","tid":1024823,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,